ul.li:
Each
event_base
structure holds a set of events and can poll to determine which events are active.

div.p:
If an event_base is set up to use locking, it is safe to access it between multiple threads. Its loop can only be run in a single thread, however. If you want to have multiple threads polling for IO, you need to
have an
event_base
for each thread.
